title: IExtrudeFeatureData2.IGetContours
description: Gets the selected contours for this extrude feature.
returns: in-process, unmanaged C++: Pointer to an array of contours ( sketch contours and sketch regions ) of size count VBA, VB.NET, C#, and C++/CLI: Not supported See In-process Methods for details about this type of method.
remarks:
Call
IExtrudeFeatureData2::GetContoursCount
before calling this method.
See
Accessing Selections that Define Features
for additional details on using this method.
